data.description: For more information on this property, contact the Listing Agent, Judy Ibrado at (520) 918-7459 or JIbrado@LongRealty.com. Enter this charming 4br/3.5ba upgraded contemporary Santa Fe style home via a generous flagstone courtyard. Upon entering you find a light & airy formal living & dining room. A generous great room w/ dramatic high ceilings & slate framed fireplace is walled w/ windows to view breathtaking sunsets. The kitchen includes granite slab counters & stacked stone encased island, double ovens & gas cook top. The roomy master suite includes large walk-in shower, garden tub, executive style counters & generous walk-in closet. Split bedrooms & baths provide ultimate privacy. Enjoy the inviting backyard w/ extended covered patio, sparkling pool, cascading water fall, gazebo & fire pit. Your large fenced-in lot highlights the pleasure of country living w/ expansive views & sunsets.
